dialog: A field without equal cultivated by the most excellent of farmers
Unfortunately, only farmers skilled enough to maintain the level of speed can sustain it.
A beatiful lake near the edge of the forest
Welcome to the plains of seasoned farmers
Fields here are well-suited towards those able to maintain them, but may do more harm than good to others
As such they require constant care for your plants otherwise they may wither
There doesn't appear to be any fish here, although that would go well with some farm grown greens
